      <description>&lt;p&gt;On October 13th 2021 I had the opportunity again to participate at &lt;a href=&#34;https://apiaddictsday.apiaddicts.org/&#34;&gt;API Addicts Days 2021&lt;/a&gt;, the biggest event of API experts in Latam and Spain.
The 1st time I explained how to build a &lt;a href=&#34;https://holisticsecurity.io/2021/06/21/un-layer4-layer7-gateway-para-proteger-tu-data&#34;&gt;Secure Data Gateway for your APIs&lt;/a&gt;, but this time I brought new concepts and approach such as The Pareto Principle and Shift-Left Testing applied to API Projects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;







    
    

