&lt;i&gt;&lt;center&gt;Minimum Viable Security, DevSecOps and API Projects&lt;/center&gt;&lt;/i&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This time I explained how to adopt the &lt;a href=&#34;https://holisticsecurity.io/2020/03/08/minimum-viable-security-for-a-k8s-webapp-tls-everywhere-part1&#34;&gt;Minimum Viable Security approach&lt;/a&gt; to implement security in the API Life cycle.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
